headline: Assessing Dell Technologies (DELL) Valuation After The Recent Share Price Pullback
summary: Dell Technologies (DELL) has drawn fresh attention after a recent pullback, with the stock showing negative returns over the past week, month, and past 3 months as investors reassess its current valuation. See our latest analysis for Dell Technologies. That recent pullback comes after a sharp swing earlier in the year, with the share price now at $124.01 and short term momentum fading even as the 1 year total shareholder return of 4.1% sits against a very large 3 year total shareholder return...
